ZH: 常识告诉我们每天要喝足够的水。
EN: Common sense tells us to drink enough water every day.

ZH: 运动是保持健康的常识。
EN: Exercise is common sense to maintain good health.

ZH: 常识告诉我们别在室内吸烟。
EN: It is common sense not to smoke indoors.

ZH: 常识告诉我们穿厚衣服在冬天会更暖和。
EN: It is common sense to wear thick clothes in winter to keep warm.

ZH: 讲卫生是社会常识。
EN: Maintaining hygiene is common sense in society.

