EN: Common sense tells us to cherish time.

ZH: 在公共场合保持整洁是一种常识。
EN: It is common sense to keep clean in public places.

ZH: 常识告诉我们要尊重长辈。
EN: Common sense tells us to respect elders.

ZH: 熄灭火源是火灾发生时的常识。
EN: Putting out the fire source is common sense when a fire occurs.
